Items.description: Barry Bonds didn't hit another home run Thursday night, but he played a part in San Francisco's go-ahead rally as the Giants beat the Los Angeles Dodgers 3-0 behind rookie Ryan Jensen.

Items.description: The last time Andy Pettitte was on the mound for New York, it was not a positive experience. On Friday, you would be hard pressed to find anything negative.

Items.description: Juan Gonzalez and all the other new faces didn't change much in Texas' home opener.

Items.vs: Toronto Blue Jays vs. Minnesota Twins

Items.description: These new-look New York Mets beat the Braves in their very first try.
